				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$\tau _{\mathrm{had}{\text {-}}\mathrm{vis}}$$\end{document} candidates. The superior four-momentum resolution from the tracking system compared to the calorimeter, for charged hadrons with transverse momentum (pT\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
